data.description: Check out this charming home located at 240 Western Avenue in Bertram, Tx. This one owner home is a 3 bedroom 2 bathroom house at just under 1200 square feet. Located in a quiet community just off of FM 243 and moments from downtown Bertram. With the current area growing this home still offers that quiet lifestyle in a country setting.
